quran[111]{c,v,t}:
  12,1,"Alif, laam, raa : nanndo …óee Aayeeje jantanooma fii mun ka fu…ó…óorde cortewol Albaqarah. ∆äee Aayeeje janngetee…óe e ngol cortewol, ko jeyaa…óe e Ayeeje Alqur'aanaare …ìanngunde nden e ko nde yowondiri e mun."
  12,2,"Menen Men jippiniriinde janngeteende e …óemngal Aarabu, belajo'o, onon Aarabu'en, on faamaay maanaaji mayre."
  12,3,"Menen Me…óen fillano maa an Nulaa…óo, ko …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥ude e fillayee, sabu goongugol …ói e hisugol konngu…ói majji e nju…ì…ìudi majji, ko Men jippiniri kon ndee Alqur'aanaare e maa…óa. Hay si a laatinoke ado jippineede nde, ko a jeyaa…óo e welsindii…ìe …ìen e oo fillayee, a anndaano fii makko."
  12,4,"Me…óen habre an Nulaa…óo, tuma nde Yuusufu maakannoo ben makko Yaaquuba: "Ko onon yo baaba'en, mi yi'i e koy…óol koode sappo e go'o, mi yi'i kadi naange ngen e lewru ndun; mi yi'i …óin fow no sujjana lam. Ngol koy…óol hari ko yacciningol wewlinirde Yuusufa (yo o his)."
  12,5,"Annabi Yaaquuba maakani …ìi…ó…óo makko on Yuusufa:Ko an yo …ìinngel am, wata a hoy…óitan musi…ó…ìe maa …ìen koy…óol maa ngol, sakko …ìe faama ngol, …ìe haasido maa, …ìe fewjane fewjoore haasidaaku ma…ì…ìe. Pellet seytaane wonannde ne…ó…óanke ko ga√±o …ìanngin…óo ngayngu."
  12,6,"Ko wano yiiru-…óaa …óin koy…ói non, Joomi maa an Yuusufa su…ìoray maa, O anndine firo koy…ói, O timmina neema Annabaaku ngun e maa…óa, wano O timminira mo e baabiraa…ìe maa …ìen …ói…óo ado maa…óa: Ibraahiima e Ishaaqa. Pellet Joomi maa ko Anndu…óo tagu Makko ngun, √ëee√±u…óo e yiilde mbo."
  12,7,"Gom…óii wonii e kabaaru Yuusufa on e musi…ó…ìe makko …ìen, taskuyeeji e waajuuji wonannde lanndotoo…ìe fii ma…ì…ìe …ìen."
  12,8,"Tuma nde musi…ó…ìe makko …ìen wi'unoo hakkunde ma…ì…ìe: "Pellet Ko Yuusufa e neene-gooto maun …ìuraa yi…óeede ka ben-men dii enen, enen le ko en jamaa …óuu…óu…ìe limoore, ko honno …ìe …ìurdinirta …ìe e dow mee…óen? Menen men yi'ii baaba'en e faljere …ìanngunde, tuma …ìe …ìurdinnoo …ìeya …ói…óo e dow amen ko aldaa e sabu fee√±u…óo."
  12,9,"Waree Yuusufa maa fero…óon mo e leydi wo…ó…óundi; yeeso ben mon ngon heeranoo on, …ìe yi…óa on giggol timmungol, wonton …ìaawo …óen kuu…óe mon- warugol mo maa feragol mon- …óon yim…ìe mo∆¥∆¥u…ìe, si on tuubi e junuubi mon …óin."
  12,10,"Gooto e musi…ó…ìe makko …ìen wi'i: Wata on waru Yuusufa, on wedduto mo ka ni…ìe woyndu yoga e setee…ìe rewoo…ìe …óon …ìen hocca-mo. Ko …óum …ìuri newaade diini warugol mo ngol, si on laatike siinu…ìe e ko wi'u…óon fii makko kon."
  12,11,"Nde …ìe fottanno pottingol mo, …ìe wi'ani ben ma…ì…ìe Yaaquuba: Ko an yo ben amen, ko he…ìu-maa a hoolotaako men e fii Yuusufa? Menen le ko men yurmetee…ìe mo, me…óen reena mo e ko lorrota mo, ko men laa…ìanoo…ìe mo reenoo…ìe mo haa o ruttora kaa maa…óa kisal. Ko ha…óata maa acciditah mo e amen?"
  12,12,"Newnan-men yaltidugol e makko janngo, o √±aama, o fija. Menen ko men reenoo…ìe mo e kala lorra memoowo mo."
  12,13,"Annabi Yaaquuba maakani …ìi…ó…ìe makko …ìen: Min no sunina lam nde yahdoton e makko; tawde mi mu√±√±otaako sertugol e makko, mi…óo hulani mo wata saafaandu(boyeeru) √±aamu-mo ka welsindor-…óon e makko √±aamugol e fija."
  12,14,"∆Åe wi'ani baaben ma…ì…ìe: Pellet si saafaandu √±aamii Yuusufa e hoore ko men jamaa …óuu…óu…ìe, haray ontuma ko men hayru…ìe …ìe mo∆¥∆¥ere alah e mu'un; tawde men ha…óaali ndu e makko."
  12,15,"Annabi Yaaquuba acci …ìe yaltidi e makko. Nde …ìe yahunoo e makko ka wo…ó…ói, …ìe fottani bugagol mo ka ni…ìe woyndu, Men wahayini e Yuusufa ontunma: Ma a yeetoyo…ìe …óee kuu…óe ma…ì…ìe hara …ìe so'aa anndude tuma yeetitoto-…óaa…ìe …óum."
  12,16,"Baaba gootoo…ìe Yuusufa …ìen arti ka ben ma…ì…ìe kiikii…óe hi…ìe woykinoo majjintina hodo ma…ì…ìe o."
  12,17,"∆Åe wi'i: Ko an yo baaben amen, menen men yehii me…óen adodnira e dogugol bugoo ndaga, men acci Yuusufa ka comci amen e ka njoo…ìa amen ko aynana men; saafaandu ndun √±aami mo. A goongintaa men non, hay si tawii ko men goongu…ìe e ko men humpitu maa kon."
  12,18,"∆Åe te≈ãtiniri fewjoore ma…ì…ìe nden ∆¥oyre: …ìe ardi e dolokke Yuusufa on hino moddiniraa ∆¥ii∆¥am goo, ∆¥aa∆¥orgol …óum batte ko saafaandu(boyeeru) ndun √±aami mo kon. Kono Annabi Yaaquuba gelorii fenaande nden ko tawi ko dolokke on seekaaki, o maakani …ìe: Wanah no sifori…óon non woniri. Ko woni goonga, ko wonkiiji mon …óin cu…óinanii on fiyaaku bon…óo, huuwu…óon mo. Fiyaaku am on non min, ko mu√±al mo∆¥∆¥al e …óum. Ko Alla woni wallinor…óo e ko sifi…óon kon fii Yuusufa."
  12,19,"Setee…ìe ari, …ìe nuli ko ∆¥oogana …ìe ndiyam, on jippini baagal makko ngal ka woyndu, Yuusufa nanngi …ìoggol ngol. Nde ∆¥oogoowo on yi'unoo mo, o weltii o wi'i: Ee welo-welo am! E hino paykum! ∆Åen ar…ìe ∆¥oogugol suu…ói mo e setee…ìe heddii…ìe …ìen, sikkugol ko o keyee(marsandiis) mo …ìe waawata yeeyude. Alla non no anndi ko …ìe wa…óata kon Yuusufa e fii suu…óugol yeeya. huunde suu…óaaki Mo e golle ma…ì…ìe …óen."
  12,20,"∆≥oogoynoo…óo on e wondii…ìe makko …ìen yeeyiroyi mo Misra coggel fam…óungel: ngel woni dirhamu-woy limotoo-koy. ∆Åe woni welsindorii…ìe e makko sabu hittingol no …ìe …ìoortondira e makko ka yaawi; tawde …ìe anndii wanaa o maccu…óo, …ìe hulani ko'e ma…ì…ìe e yim…ìe makko …ìen. ∆äum ko hattirde e yurmeende Alla nden e makko, fii wata …ìe nee…ìidu e makko."
  12,21,"Gorko soodu…óo mo on Misra wi'ani …ìeyngu makko: Teddin jipporde makko nden, mo∆¥∆¥o-…óaa e makko; hino gasa ka o nafira en wallitorgol en yoga e golleeji men maa jogito…óen mo …ìi…ó…óo ne'etee…óo. Ko wano Men da…óndiri non Yuusufa e maayde, Men yaltini mo ka woyndu, Men humindiri …ìernde gorko on e makko; ko non kadi Men ho…óniri mo Misra fii yo Men anndin mo firo koy…ói. Alla non ko foolu…óo e fiyaaku makko on: …óum ko laatotoo…óum, alah firtinoowo Mo. Kono …ìur…ìe …óuu…óu…ìe e yim…ìe …ìen -woni heefer…ìe …ìen- anaadah …óum."
  12,22,"Nde Yuusufa yottinoo sagatalaaku makko ngun, Men okki mo faamu e anndal. Ko wano ndii njo…ìdi …óon Men yo…ìirta mo∆¥∆¥inoo…ìe …ìen ka rewugol Alla."
  12,23,"Debbo laam…óo on …óa…ì…ìiri Yuusufa e newaare fii fijirde. O soki baafe …óen no …ìe yeewra, o wi'i: "Aru e am!" Yuusufu maaki: "Mi moolorii Alla e ko noddataa lam e mun kon. Pellet Jey…óo lam on mo∆¥∆¥inii weerde am nde ka makko, mi janfotaako mo. Si mi janfike mo, haray mi too√±ii. Pellet too√±oo…ìe …ìen maletaake."
  12,24,"Gom…óii debbo on himmirii wa…óugol faahisaaku ngun. ∆äum kadi ari e miijo oya si wanaano o yi'ii e Aayeeje Alla …óen ko ha…óata mo e …óum wo…ó…óina mo e mun. Men hollirii mo …óe fii no Men yiltira mo e bone, Men wo…ó…óindina mo e jeeno e jenfa. Pellet Yuusufa ko jeyaa…óo e jeyaa…ìe amen su…ìiraa…ìe Nulal e Annabaaku."
  12,25,"∆Åe …ói…óo kala …ìe adondiri ka baafal: Yuusufa hari ko no da…óndira hoore-mun, debbo on kan ko fii ha…óugol mo yaltugol. O nanngi dolokke makko fii wata o yaltu, o seekiri mo …ìaawo. ∆Åe tawi moodi makko ka baafal. Debbo on wowlirani moodi mun ∆¥o∆¥re: Lepte alanaa on faalanaa…óo …ìeyngu maa bonki si wanaa kaso maa o leptiree lepte muusu…óe."
  12,26,"Yuusufa maaki: Ko kanko …óa…ì…ìiri lam bonki, mi ja…ìanaali mo. Alla wa…ói suko jeyaakun e yim…ìe debbo on wowli ka tiggu, ko seedorii wiide: Si tawii dolokke Yuusufa on o yeeso seekiraa, …óum hollii haray debbo on goongii; tawde hari o salantono mo woni, kanko gorko on hray o fenay."
  12,27,"Si tawii non dolokke makko on ko …ìaawo seekiraa, …óum hollii haray gorko on goongii; tawde haray ko debbo wonunoo …óa…ì…ìirde mo bone, kanko himo dogude mo, debbo on ko fenu…óo."
  12,28,"Nde moodi makko yi'unoo dolokke Yuusufa on ko vaawo seekiraa, o yananaa e goonga Yuusufa kan, o wi': Ngol tukkugol maa …óoo ko jeyaa…óum e pewje mon, onon rew…ìe …ìen. Pellet pewje mon …óen ko tii…óu…óe."
  12,29,"O wi'ani Yuusufa: Ko an yo Yuusufa, yejjitu fii …óum …óoo, wata a yeetito gooto. An debbo on, …óa…ì…ìir Joomi maa haforaneede junuubi maa …óin; tawde pellet a jeyaama e bakkondim…ìe …ìen sabu …óa…ì…ìirgol maa Yuusufa fii bonki."
  12,30,"Kabaaru debbo on saakitii e saare nden. Rew…ìe goo wi'iri ≈ãi√±ere: Debbo laam…óo on …óa…ì…ìirii kurkaadu makko ndun hoore-mun. Gom…óii giggol ngol …ìurtirii mo ka …ìernde. Menen dey me…óen yi'ira oo debbo sabu ngol …óa…ì…ìirgol mo e yi…óugol mo oo suka kurkaadu makko, e majjere …ìanngunde."
  12,31,"Nde …ìeyngu laam…óo on nanunoo rew…ìe …ìen …ìe √±o'irii mo ≈ãi√±ugol kuu…óe makko …óen, o nelani …ìe fii yi'ugol Yuusufa no …ìe okki-mo ngantu. O hebilani …ìe nda…óundi e ngawluuji, o jonni gooto kala e ma…ì…ìe e la…ìi ko lesira, o wi'ani Yuusufa (yo o his): Yatlu e ma…ì…ìe. Nde …ìe ndaarunoo mo, …ìe ≈ãal…ói e ≈ãari makko kin, …ìe hetti juu…óe …óen hakkee ko haa- waa-mbo. ∆Åe wi'i: Kaawee Alla! Oo suka wanaa …ìanndinke. Kii ≈ãari makko …óoo hebilanaaka …ìanndinke. Oo wonaali si wanaa malaa'ikaajo teddu…óo jeyaa…óo teddu…ìe …ìen."
  12,32,"Debbo laam…óo on wi'ani rew…ìe …ìen …ìaawo o yi'ii ko he…ìi …ìen kon : Ko oo suka felir…óon lam giggol mun. Gom…óii mi …óa…ì…ìirii mo bonki o ha…óitii. Si tawii o wa…óaali ko mi …óa…ì…ìiri mo kon, ma o naatu kaso ma o jeye kadi e hoy…ìe …ìen."
  12,33,"Yuusufa (yo o his) maaki himo toroo Joomi makko: Joomi am, ko kammbol kaso ngol …ìurani lam e ko …ìe noddata lam e mun kon e fijirde. Si a huncaali ittu…óaa lam e pewje ma…ì…ìe …óen, mi oo√±oto e ma…ì…ìe, mi jeyee e majju…ìe …ìen, mi wa…óa faale ma…ì…ìe on."
  12,34,"Alla jaabinani mo toraare makko nden, O huncani mo pewje debbo laam…óo on e rew…ìe saare nden. Pellet, Ko kanko Senii…óo On woni Nanoowo toraare Yuusufa nden e kala toraare, Anndu…óo fiyaaku makko e kala fiyaaku."
  12,35,"Refti nde debbo laam…óo on e yim…ìe ma…ì…ìe …ìen yi'unoo maandeeji la…ì…ìin…ói Yuusufa …óin, wonnde bee o sokee -fii wata …ìe wirto- haa e dumunna."
  12,36,"∆Åe soki mo. Sukaa…ìe …ói…óo naatidi e makko ka kaso. Gooto e ma…ì…ìe wi'ani yuusufa: Min mi hoy…óii mi…óo siiwa 'inau fii sanngara. ∆äi…ómo on wi'i: Min mi hoy…óii mi…óo roondii cobbal ka hoore-am, colli no √±aama e maggal. Humpitii men, an Yuusufa, firo koy…ói amen. Menen men yi'ii ma jeyaa…óo e mo∆¥∆¥inoo…ìe …ìen."
  12,37,"Yuusufu maaki: √ëaametee ardirantah on laam…óo on maa go…ó…óo goo si wanaa mi yeetoto on haqiiqa e kayfiya …óum ado o arde on. Ngol firtugol koy…ói ko jeyaa…óum e ko Joomi am anndini lam, wanaa ndaaro maa ko nanndi e mun. Mi …óalii diina yim…ìe …ìe gom…óinaa Alla, haray kam…ìe e fii laakara on ko …ìe yeddu…ìe."
  12,38,"Jokkumi diina baabiraa…ìe am …ìen: Ibraahiimaa e Ishaaqa e Yaaquuba; ko kan woni diina bajjin…óingol Alla. Sellantaa men nde men kafidata e Alla go…ó…óum goo. Ko Kanko woni heeror…óo gootaagu. On tawhiidi e gom…óinal ko mi woni e mun min e baabiraa…ìe am …ìen, ko jeyaa…óum e …ìural Alla e dow amen nde O hawrindini men e …óum. Jeyaa…óum kadi e …ìural Makko e dow yim…ìe …ìen fow nde tawnoo O imminii Annabaa…ìe e ma…ì…ìe; kono ko …ìuri …óuu…óude e yim…ìe …ìen …ìe yettatah Alla e neemaaji Makko …óin, ko yeddugol Mo …ìe wa…óata."
  12,39,"Refti Yuusufa yewti sukaa…ìe …ìen …ói…óo ka kaso o maakani …ìe: E ko rewugol rewetee…ói sertu…ói …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥ude, kaa ko rewugol Alla Gooto Mo alaa kafidii…óo On, On Foolu…óo tanaa Mun, Mo fooletaake?"
  12,40,"On alaa e rewde gaanin Alla, si wanaa in…óe …óe hikkaaki nokku, …óe innitir…óon onon e baabiraa…ìe mon rewetee…óe, …óe alah non huunde e ge…ìal ka reweede, Alla jippinanaali kon ko innitir…óon …óe hujja tinndinoowo sellugol …óe. √ëaawoore tagu ngun fow alanaa si wanaa Alla gooto On, wanah …óee in…óe …óe innitir…óon onon e baabiraa…ìe mon. Alla yamirii on nde bajjin…óinirton Mo dewal, O ha…ói on kafidugol Mo e go…ó…óum goo. Ko …óum woni diina √±ii…ìuka ka oo√±aare alaa e mu'un; kono ko …ìuri …óuu…óude e yim…ìe …ìen anndaa …óum, ko …óum wa…ói si …ìe sirkannde Alla, …ìe rewa tagaa…ói goo."
  12,41,"Ko onon yo wondii…ìe am …ói…óo ka kaso! Yi'u…óo e mon on no hama inbu, o yaltay woni ka kaso, o yiltitoo e golle makko, o yarna laam…óo on. Oya yi'u…óo cobbal ngal ka hoore-mun colli no √±aama e maggal, ko waretee…óo fetee, colli …óin √±aama teewu hoore makko nden. Fiyaaku mo lanndi…óon fii mun on √±aawaama gasii. ∆äum ko wa…óay…óum feere alaa."
  12,42,"Yuusufu maakani on mo o sikki da…óay e ma…ì…ìe kam…ìe …ói…óo -onon woni yarnoowo laam…óo on-: Janto fii am ka laam…óo on, hino gasa ka o yaltina lam ka kaso. Seytaane yejjntini yarnoowo on jantagol fii Yuusufa ka laam…óo on. Yuusufa √±ii…ìiti ka kaso …ìaawo …óum, yoga e duu…ìi."
  12,43,"Laam…óo on wi'i: Min mi yi'ii e koy…óol na'i jee…ói…ói fay…ói, na nyaama foo∆¥u…ói jee…ói…ói …óin. Mi yi'ii kadi butaali jee…ói…ói kecce e yooru…óe jee…ói…ói. Ko onon yo mbatu dental, humpitee lam firo ngol koy…óol, si on laatike anndu…ìe firo koy…ói."
  12,44,"∆Åe wi'i: Koy…ói maa …óin ko jii…ìu-jaa…ìa. Kala ko wa'i non, haray alaa firo. Men wonaali non anndu…ìe firo koy…ói jii…ìu-jaa…ìu."
  12,45,"On yarnoowo da…óunoo…óo on e sukaa…ìe …ìen …ói…óo ka kaso annditi Annabi Yuusufa ka firo koy…ói …ìaawo dumunna, o wi'i: Min mi humpitay on firo koy…óol laam…óo on si mi lanndike anndu…óo fii mun. Laam…óo on, nulee lam ka Yuusufa o firana on koy…óol ngol."
  12,46,"Nde on da…óu…óo hewtunoo ka Yuusufa, o wi'ani mo: Ko an yo Yuusufa, an goongu…óo! Humpitii men firo hoy…óu…óo na'i jee…ói…ói fay…ói na nyaama foo∆¥u…ói jee…ói…ói …óin. O yi'ii kadi butaali jee…ói…ói kecci e yooru…óe jee…ói…ói. Belajo'o, …ìe ruttoto ka laam…óo on e yim…ìe makko …ìen, belajo'o, …ìe annda firo koy…óol laam…óo on, …ìe annda kadi …ìural maa ngal e darja maa on."
  12,47,"Yuusufu (yo o his) maakani …ìe ka firo koy…óol: On remay duu…ìi jee…ói…ói jokkindinon e tii…ónaare: Ko so√±oton kon e hitaande kala nder …óin duu…ìi jee…ói…ói, accon …óum ka dukkal(wutaandu) mun fii wata fuunu, si wanaa see…óa e ko gabbe ko hatonjinoyton fii √±aamugol."
  12,48,"Refti aroyay …ìaawo …óin duu…ìi jee…ói…ói sa…ótu…ói …ói remu…óon e muu…óum, duu…ìi jee…ói…ói maapunde(yoo-, …ói yim…ìe …ìen √±aamata e majji kala ko so√±anoo e …óiya duu…ìi sa…ótu…ói si wanah see…óa e kon ko maru…óon fii awdi."
  12,49,"Refti aroyay …ìaawo …óin duu…ìi yoor, hitaande nde to…ìo jippotoo e mun, pu…ói …óin yalta, yim…ìe …ìen siiwa kala ko …ìe hatonjini e muu…óum; wano inabu e nebban-le…ó…óe e le…ó…óe-sukkar."
  12,50,"Nde …ìe yottinnoo ko Yuusufu firtani koy…óol ngol kon, laam…óo on wi'ani golloo…ìe mun …ìen: Yaltinee mo ka kaso addanon lam mo. Nde imminaa…óo laam…óo on arunoo ka Yuusufa, o maakani on: Rutto ka koohoojo maa on lanndo…óaa mo fiyaaku rew…ìe barminnoo…ìe juu…óe mon …óen? ∆äum ko fii no o fe√±√±inira o bonnah ado o yaltineede ka kaso. Pellet, Joomi am hino anndi ko …ìe huuwi kon e …óa…ì…ìirgol lam bonki. Huunde suu…óaaki Mo e …óum."
  12,51,"Laam…óo o wii rew…ìe …ìe hol ko he…ìi mon haa …óa…ì…ìir…óon Yuusuf feere bonnde haa o wa…óda e mon ko boni, rew…ìe …ìe mbii laam…óo o Yuusuf ina wo…ó…ói ko O tuuma ko, min ngoondiri Alla min nganndah e Makko bonannde, ndeen tan Cuddii…óo Laam…óo o wii jooni de goongo …ìanngi ko miin hoomtatnoo mbo, wonah kanko hoomtatnoo mi, ko goongo o haali ko o noddatii ko, te hombo hisi ko o tuuma ko."
  12,52,"∆Åeyngu laam…óo on wi'i: Ko fii yo Yuusufa anndu ko mi qirritanii wonnde ko mi …óa…ì…ìi mo, e wonnde ko goonga makko wiide mi fenaali e hoore-makko …ìaawo makko. Tabitanii lam e ko fe∆¥∆¥i kon wonnde Alla fewnatah fenoowo hodoowo."
  12,53,"∆Åeyngu laam…óo on jokkitii o wi'i: Mi la…ì…ìinaa hoore-am e faandanagol bone, mi faandoraaki …óum kadi la…ì…ìingol hoore-am; sabu wonkii ne…ó…óanke ko heewuki yamirde bone, tawde ki oo√±oray e ko welataki, yiltugol ki e …óum sa…óta, si wanaa kin ki Alla yurmaa, O da…ónda ki e yamirgol bone. Pellet Joomi am ko Haforanoowo kala tuubu…óo e jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen, Hinnotoo…óo …ìe."
  12,54,"Nde laa…ìugol Yuusufa ngol e ganndal makko fee√±unoo, laam…óo on wi'ani golloowo mun …ìen: Addanee lam mo, mi heertinana mo hoore-am. ∆Åe addi mo. Nde o yewtunoo mo, ganndal oya ngal e haqqille makko …óen …ìanngani mo, o wi'ani mo: An on Yuusufa, a wonii hannde ka amen, jom-nokku e jaahu, hoolaa…óo."
  12,55,"Annabi Yuusufa maaki: "Halfinam reenugol ngaluuji jawle …óen e √±aameteeji leydi Misra ndin, min ko mi reenoowo hoolnii…óo, anndu…óo ko mi wa…óata."
  12,56,"Ko wano Men neeminirnoo non e Yuusufa la…ì…ìingol mo …ìoortindira mo e kaso, Men neeminiri e makko √±imnugol ka leydi Misra, himo jippoo ho…óa e mayri nokku kala ka o yi…ói. Me…óen ye…óa yurmeendeAa Amen nden aduna on mo Men muuyi e jeyaa…ìe Amen …ìen. Men yeebataa njo…ìdi mo∆¥∆¥inoo…ìe …ìen, ko Men timminiroo…ìe ndi ko aldaa e …óuytugol."
  12,57,"Pellet ko mbarjaari ndi Alla hebili ndin laakara …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥ude diini njo…ìdi aduna ndin, wonannde …ìen gom…óim…ìe Alla …ìe laatii huliroo…ìe Mo …óoftagol yamirooje Makko wo…ó…óitoo ha…óaa…ói Makko."
  12,58,"Baaba-gootoo…ìe Yuusufa …ìen ardiri Misra e ko yeeyetee, …ìe naati ka makko. O anndi ko baaba-gootoo…ìe makko …ìen nii, kono kam…ìe …ìe annditaali mo; tawde dumunna on juutii kadi mbaadi makko ndin waylike, hari ko o cukalel fewno ko …ìe buginoo mo ka woyndu."
  12,59,"Tuma o jonnunoo…ìe ko …ìe lanndii kon e gabbe e njoo…ìa, …ìe humpiti mo wonnde hi…ìe mari musi…ó…óo baaba-gootoojo mo …ìe acci ka ben mun, o maakani …ìe: addanee lam musi…ó…óo mon baaba-gooto, mi …ìeydana on ko ngelooba ronndoo. E on yi'aali wonnde mi…óo timmina …ìetu ngun Mi alaa e …óuytude, e wonnde ko mi mo∆¥∆¥o weernoo…ìe …ìen?"
  12,60,"Si on addanaali lam mo, haray fenaande mon nden …ìanngii wiide hi…óon mari musi…ó…óo baaba-gooto. Mi …ìetitantaa on √±aametee, wata on …ìado kadi leydi am ndin."
  12,61,"Baaba-gootoo…ìe makko …ìen jaabii mo: Men …óa…ì…ìiray mo ben makko, men etoo fii mun. Menen ko men golloo…ìe kon ko yamir-…óaa men ko aldaa e ra…ì…ìindinagol."
  12,62,"Yuusufu maakani golloo…ìe makko …ìen: Jonnitee …ìee do≈ãlle ma…ì…ìe …óen fii no …ìe annditiroya tuma ruttii ka yim…ìe ma…ì…ìe …ìe wonnde e soondanaano …ìe, …óum wa…óay …ìe yiltioo hara ontuma hi…ìe wonndi e musi…ó…óo ma…ì…ìe on. ∆äum ko fii no …ìe tabintirina Yuusufa goonga ma…ì…ìe kan, o ja…ìana …ìe do≈ãlle ma…ì…ìe …óen."
  12,63,"Tuma nde …ìe ruttinoo ka ben ma…ì…ìe, …ìe fillanii mo ko Yuusufa teddini …ìe kon, …ìe wi'i: Ko an yo …ìen amen, men salante …ìetu si men yahdaali e musi…ó…óo amen on, immindin mo e amen. Si a immindinii men, men …ìetante. Men fodii ma reenugol mo ruttoda e makko himo hisi."
  12,64,"Ben ma…ì…ìe maakani …ìe: hara mi hooloray on e fii makko, si wanaa no mi hoolornoo non e neene-gooto makko on Yuusufa oya tuma? Mi hoolino on e fii on …óon, fodu…óon lam reenugol mo, on hunnaali ahdi. Hoolaare alanaa on ka an wonnde on reenay mo, ko Alla mi hoolori; ko Kanko woni mo∆¥∆¥o reenoowo on mo O yi…ói reenude, …ìur…óo mo∆¥∆¥ude yurmetee…ìe …ìen, wonannde mo O yi…ói yurmeede."
  12,65,"Nde …ìe udditunoo do≈ãlle ma…ì…ìe √±aametee …óen …óe …ìe addori, …ìe tawi coggeeli mun …óin ruttitaama e ma…ì…ìe. ∆Åe wi'ani ben ma…ì…ìe: E ko men …óa…ì…ìata …ìuri ngal teddungal …óoo? ∆äum …óoo ko coggu √±aametee amen on, laam…óo on jonnitirii men …óum teddingol men. Men addanay yim…ìe amen …ìen √±aametee, men reena musi…ó…óo amen on e ko hulan-…óaa mo kon, men …ìeydora …ìetu ngelooba tawde mba ronndannto men; …ìeydorgol …ìetu ngelooba, ko huunde newiinde ka laam…óo on."
  12,66,"Ben ma…ì…ìe maakani …ìe: Mi immindintaa mo e moo…óon haa ∆¥ettanon mi ahadi ka Alla, wonnde pellet on artiranay lam mo si wanaa hara maayde hu…ìindi on fow mon, hara alah heddii…óo e mon, on ronku feere ha…óugol …óum. ∆Åaawo …ìe ∆¥ettanii mo ahdi Alla fellintinaandi e …óum ndin, o maaki: Alla ko seedii…óo e ko wowlu…óen kon, seedee Makko on yonii en."
  12,67,"Ben ma…ì…ìe maakani …ìe hino wasiyoo …ìe: wata on naatiroy Misra e damal gootal hi…óon wonndi, ko yo on naatir e dame seertu…óe. Ko …óum …ìurata hisinnde on diini go…ó…óo huu…ìitirta on lorra si o immanike on. Mi alaa wowlirannde on …óum, fii du√±angol on lorra mo Alla faandorii on, wanaa kadi fii poo…óangol on nafa mo Alla yi…óanaa on. √ëaawoore alaa si wanaa √±aawoore Alla nden, fiyaaku alaa si wanaa fiyaaku Makko on. Ko e Makko fawii-mi e kala fiyaaku am, ko e Makko Kanko tun, yo fawo fawotoo…ìe …ìen e fiyakuuji ma…ì…ìe …óin."
  12,68,"∆Åe yahdi e neene-gooto oya on. Nde …ìe naatirnoo e dame seertu…óe, wano ben ma…ì…ìe yamirnoo…ìe non, …óum wonaano hino du√±ana …ìe huunde e ko Alla muuyani …ìe kon. ∆äum ko annde Yaaquuba tun fii …ìi…ó…ìe makko …ìen o fe√±√±ini, o wasiyii …ìe …óum e hoore himo anndi √±aawoore alaa si wanaa √±aawoore Alla nden. Ko o anndu…óo ko men anndini mo kon e gom…óingol hoddiraaji e jogitagol sabuuji …óin. Kono ko …ìuri …óuu…óude e yim…ìe …ìen …ìe anndaa …óum."
  12,69,"Nde …ìe baaba-gootoo…ìe Yuusufa …ìen naatunoo ka makko hi…ìe wonndi e neene-gooto makko on, o …ìanniti neene-gooto makko on e makko, o maakini mo sirru: ko min woni neene-gooto maa on Yuusuf. wata a sunor piiji kaanu…ói …ói musi…ó…ìe maa …ìen huuwaynoo, immorde lorra e ngayngu hoore-men, e ko …ìe werlii lam kon ka woyndu."
  12,70,"Nde Yuusufu yamirnoo golloo…ìe makko rimndude ngelooba musi…ó…ìe makko …ìen √±aametee,o wa…ói etirgal laam…óo o etiraynoo ngal ka do≈ãngal neene gooto makko on …ìe anndaali,fii no on heddora e takko makko.Nde …ìe fokkiti yiltitagol ka ma…ì…ìe noddoowo ewnii …ìe:Ko onon yo joomiraa…ìe ngelooba roondinba √±aametee, ko on wuy…ìe ."
  12,71,"Musi…ó…ìe Yuusufa …ìen fewtiti e ewnii…óo on e wonndu…ìe e makko …ìen …ìe wi'i: Ko hon…óum majjiri on haa tuumiron min nguyka?"
  12,72,"Ewnii…óo on e wonndii…ìe makko …ìen wi'ani Yuusufa: Sari'yaare nde laam…óo on etirta nden majjirii men. Hino woodani kala addu…óo nde ado wi√±eede, yeru do≈ãngal ngelooba. Ko min fawtanii mo …óum."
  12,73,"Musi…ó…ìe Yuusufa …ìen wi'ani …ìe: Men woondirii Alla, gom…óii hi…óon anndi laa…ìugol amen e wo…ó…óondirgol amen e …óum, wano rentir…óon men. Hi…óon anndi kadi men ardaali ka leydi Msira fii bonnugol, men mee…óaali wonnde wuy…ìe e nguurndam amen."
  12,74,"Ewnii…óo on e wonndii…ìe makko …ìen wi'i: Ko hon…óum wonata njo…ìdi wujju…óo on e moo…óon si tawii ko on fenu…ìe e ko wii…óon kon hi…óon laa…ìi e wujjugol?"
  12,75,"Musi…ó…ìe Yuusufa …ìen wi'ani …ìe: Njo…ìdi wujju…óo woo e amen: wonnde kala mo ko wujjaa kon tawaa ka do≈ãngal mun, o jonnitay hoore-makko wujjaa…óo on fii ko maccin…óina mo. Ko wano ndin njo…ìdi maccin…óingol …óon men yo…ìitirta wuy…ìe …ìen."
  12,76,"∆Åe artiri …ìe ka Yuusufu fii wittugol do≈ãlle baaba-gootoo…ìe makko …ìen ado neene-gooto makko on fii suu…óugol feere nden. Refti o li√±citi do≈ãngal neene-gooto makko on, o yaltini ton sariyaare laam…óo on. Ko wano Men fewjirani Yuusufa non feere wa…óugol sariyaare nden ka do≈ãngal neene-gooto makko on, men fewjirani mo kadi nanngitirgol musi…ó…ìe makko …ìen √±aawoore leydi ma…ì…ìe ndin, maccin…óingol wujju…óo on. Si …ìe gollitirno √±aawoore leydi laam…óo on Misra e hoore wujju…óo on, …ìe huutoray piggal e koondugol, si wanaa hara ko Alla muuyi feere goo, tawde ko O hattan…óo …óum. Me…óen …ìanta martabaaji on mo Men muuyani e jeyaa…ìe Amen …ìen, wano Men …ìantiri darja Yuusufa. Hino e dow kala jom-ganndal, ganndo goo …ìur…óo mo; hino e dow ganndal fow ngal kadi, ganndal Alla On anndu…óo kala huunde."
  12,77,"Musi…ó…ìe Yuusufa …ìen wi'i: Si o wujjii, haawnaaki, tawde neene-gooto makko on wujjiino ado oo …óoo wujjude -…ìe faandori …óum Yuusufa (yo o his)- Yuusufa suu…ói mette mum e konngol ma…ì…ìe ngol kon ka wonkii makko, o fe√±√±inanaali …ìe …óum, o maaki e wonkii makko: Ko ngayngu mon ngun e kuu…óe mon bon…óe …óen ado hannde, woni bone on tigiri e oo nokku. Ko Alla non …ìuri anndude ndee fefindaare mon yaltunde e mon."
  12,78,"Musi…ó…ìe Yuusufa …ìen wi'ani mo: Ko an yo laam…óo on, oo no mari baabiraawo nayeeje …óoggos mo o yi…ói mo∆¥∆¥a. ∆≥ettu gooto e amen lonto makko. Menen men yi'ii ma jeyaa…óo e mo∆¥∆¥inoo…ìe gollodal amen e wo…ó…ìe goo. Mo∆¥∆¥an …óum …óon e amen."
  12,79,"Annabi Yuusufa maaki: Yo Alla da…óndu men too√±ude da…óndii…óo ko o wa…óaa. Men nannga mo jogitaaki sariyaare laam…óo on ka do≈ãngal mun. Haray ontuma men wonii too√±u…ìe, tawde men le…ì- tii da…óndii…óo, men acci bon…óo on."
  12,80,"Nde …ìe ta∆¥inoo e jaabawol Yuusufa ngol e ko …óa…ì…ìi kon, …ìe ndeesti yim…ìe …ìen fii diisondiral. Maw…óo ma…ì…ìe on wi'i: Mi…óo anndintina on wonnde ben mon ∆¥ettoduno e mon ahadi ka Alla, wonnde on artiray …ìi…ó…óo makko on si wanaa hara on huu…ìitira ko on hattanaa du√±ugol …óum. Annditon kadi ko welsindino…óon e Yuusufa kon, ronku…óon hunnude ahadi mon ndin e ben mon. Min on mi yaltataa Misra haa ben am du≈ãanoo lam ruttagol maa Alla √±aawana lam yahdugol e musi…ó…óo am on. Ko Kanko Alla …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥ude e √±aawoo…ìe …ìen, ko goonga e nun…óal O √±aawirta."
  12,81,"Kotiraawo maw…óo on wi'i: Ruttee ka ben mon, wi'anon mo: ∆Åi…ó…óo maa on wujjii, laam…óo Misra on maccin…óinirii mo lepte nguyka makko kan. Men humpitaa ma non si wanaa ko men anndi e huunde nde men seedorii yaltineede sariyaare laam…óo on ka do≈ãngal …ìi…ó…óo maa on. Men anndaano o wujjay, si me…óen annduno …óum, men ahodataano e maa…óa artirgol mo."
  12,82,"Si a hoolaaki men, an ben amen, lanndo yim…ìe Misra …ìen …ìe men wonunoo ka mun e lappol setee…ìe …ìe men ardunoo e mun …ìen, …ìe humpitete ko men humpitu maa kon. Pellet ko men goongu…ìe e ko men humpitir-maa nguyka makko kan."
  12,83,"Ben ma…ì…ìe Yaaquuba maakani …ìe: Wanaa non woniri. Ko woni goonga, ko wonnde wonkiiji mon …óin cu…óanii on fewjangol mo wano fewjiranno…óon neene-gooto makko on Yuusufa aranun. Mi mu√±√±orii no labiraa, ko aldaa e wullitagol si wanaa e Alla. Hino hasii ka Alla artiranta mi …ìe, …ìe fow ma…ì…ìe: Yuusufu e neene-gooto makko mun on e kotoo ma…ì…ìe maw…óo on. Pellet Kanko Senii…óo On, ko O Anndu…óo fiyaaku am, √ëee√±u…óo e toppitagol fiyaaku am."
  12,84,"O huccitiri …óuurnagol e ma…ì…ìe, o maaki: Ee tii…óugol sunaare am e fii Yuusufa! ∆Åale-…ìale gita makko …óen rawniri suno, hakkee ko o wulli mo kon. Hari ko o …ìennu…óo suno e …ìi…óaare, kono o …ìenni …óum e yim…ìe …ìen."
  12,85,"Musi…ó…ìe Yuusufa …ìen wi'ani …ìen ma…ì…ìe: Men woondirii Alla, an ben amen, a seerataa hi…óa janntoo fii Yuusufa, haa nawna foole maa maaya tigiri."
  12,86,"Ben ma…ì…ìe maakani …ìe: Mi wullitortaa annde am e sunaare am, si wanaa e Alla tun. Mi…óo anndi e mo∆¥∆¥ere Alla nden, e ko O jaabinanta kon maapii…óo, e ko O yo…ìata kon ke…ìaa…óo musiiba ko on anndaa onon."
  12,87,"Ben ma…ì…ìe maakani …ìe: Ko onon yo …ìi…ó…ìe am, yehee tefoyon fii Yuusufa e mi√±an-mun. Wata on ta∆¥o e ko Alla yurmetee kon jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen. Ko fii, ta∆¥otaako e yurmeende Alla nden si wanaa yim…ìe heeferee…ìe …ìen; tawde ko …ìe majjaa…ìe kattal Alla mawngal ngal, e …ìural Makko suu…óiingal e jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen."
  12,88,"∆Åe wa…ói ko …ìen ma…ì…ìe yamiri …ìe kon, …ìe yehi …óa…ì…ìitugol Yuusufa e mi√±an-mun. Nde …ìe naatunoo ka Yuusufa, …ìe wi'ani mo: Tammpere e baasal he…ìii men. Men ardii e sil'a jaasu…óo fan…óu…óo. Etan-men ko timmi, wano etiranayno-…óaa men aranun, sakko-…óaa e amen ko …ìeydii kon e …óum maa sulfiraneede si'la amen fan…óu…óo on. Pellet, Alla yo…ìitiray sakko- too…ìe …ìen ko …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥ude e njo…ìdi."
  12,89,"Nde o nanunoo haala ma…ì…ìe kan, o yurmaa …ìe, o anndintinori e ma…ì…ìe wiide …ìe: Hara on annditii ko wa…óuno…óon Yuusufa e neene-gooto makko on fewndo wonuno…óon majju…ìe e battane kuu…óe mon …óen e ma…ì…ìe?"
  12,90,"∆Åe ≈ãal…ói, …ìe wi'i: Kere ko an woni Yuusufa? Yuusufu maakani …ìe: Eyyo, ko min woni Yuusufa. Oo mo suti…óon …óoo takko am, ko neene-gooto am. Gom…óii Alla mo∆¥∆¥orike e amen …ìoortugol e ko men na…ìidi e mun, O …ìamta fii amen. Ko fii, kala hulir…óo Alla …óoftagol yamirooje Makko …óen, wo…ó…óitoo ha…óaa…ói Makko …óin, o mu√±√±ii jarrabuyee, pellet, golle makko …óen e mo∆¥∆¥ere jeyaa. Alla non yeebataa njo…ìdi mo∆¥∆¥inoo…ìe …ìen, ko O reenoowo …ìe ndi."
  12,91,"Musi…ó…ìe makko …ìen wi'ani mo hi…ìe ngantinoo e kuu…óe ma…ì…ìe: Men woondirii Alla, Alla …ìurnirii ma e amen ye…óugol ma jikkuuji timmu…ói. Pellet, men woniino e kon ko men wa…óu-maa, ko men bonnu…ìe e maa…óa too√±u…ìe ma."
  12,92,"Yuusufu ja…ìani …ìe nga≈ãto, o maaki: Feloore alaa e hoore-mon hannde. On feletaake on ≈ãi√±etaake. Yo Alla yaafano on. Ko Kanko woni Mo∆¥∆¥oo Yurmetee…óo."
  12,93,"Nde o humpitinoo ko he…ìi ben makko kon e wumugol, o jonni …ìe dolokke makko on, o maaki: Yahdee e oo dolokke am …óoo, bugo…óon mo ka yeeso baaben am, …ìe wattay yi'ude. Addanon lam …ìeynguure mon nden …ìe fow ma…ì…ìe."
  12,94,"Nde lappol setee…ìe …ìen yaltunoo Misra, …ìe wo…ó…ótii saare nden, Annabi Yaaquuba maakani …ìi…ó…ìe makko …ìen e won…ìe ka leydi makko …ìen: Min mi…óo he…ìa balangol Yuusufa, sinno wanaa fii yo …óaytinam, w'ion mi…óo wowla ko mi anndaa."
  12,95,"∆Åi…ó…ìe makko wonunoo…ìe …óon …ìen wi'i: Men woondirii Alla, an on a seeraali e majjere maa …ìooyunde nden e fii Yuusufa wonnde hino hasii ka yiitaa mo."
  12,96,"Nde humpitoowo Yaaquuba on ko welata mo arunoo, o werlii dolokke Yuusufa on ka yeeso makko, o wonti yi'oowo. O maakani …ìi…ó…ìe makko …ìen: E mi yeetanooki on mi…óo anndi e neweende Alla nden e mo∆¥∆¥ere Makko nden ko on anndaa onon?"
  12,97,"∆Åi…ó…ìe makko …ìen ngatinanii ben ma…ì…ìe Yaaquuba (yo o his) ko …ìe wa…ói kon Yuusufa e mi√±an-mun, …ìe wi'i: Ko an yo ben amen, …óa…ì…ìiran-men ka Alla haforaneede junuubi amen yawtu…ói …óin. Menen men laatinoke junubante bonnu…ìe e ko men wa…ói kon Yuusufa e neene-gooto makko on."
  12,98,"Ben ma…ì…ìe maakani …ìe: Aray ka mi …óa…ì…ìirana on Joomi am haforannede. Ko Kanko woni Haforoowo junuubi tuuboo…ìe …ìen e jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen, Hinnotoo…óo …ìe."
  12,99,"Annabi Yaaquuba yaltidi e …ìeynguure makko nden ka leydi ma…ì…ìe, …ìe sutii ka Yuusufu Misra. Nde …ìe naatunoo ka makko, o …ìattiniti maw…ìe makko …ìen …ói…óo e makko, o maakani musi…ó…ìe makko …ìen e …ìeynguure ma…ì…ìe nden: Naatiree Misra muuy…óe Alla, ko on hoolii…ìe, bone woo memataa on."
  12,100,"O toolni maw…ìe makko …ìen …ói…óo ka danki makko, ontuma …ìe hiwrori mo kam…ìe e musi…ó…ìe makko …ìen sappo e go'o sujjugol. Ngol sujjugol wanaa dewal, ko teddungal, yahdungol e yamiroore Alla nden wano ardiri non ka koy…óol. Ko …óum wa…ói si Yuusufa maakani ben makko: Ngol hiwrorgol lam …óoo sujjugol, ko firo koy…óol am ngol oya tuma ngol mi fillaninoo on. Gom…óii Joomi am wa…óii ngol goonga, O mo∆¥∆¥ike kadi e am tuma O yaltinnoo lam ka kaso O itti on onon kadi ka ladde, …ìaawo nde seytaane bonni hakkunde am e musi…ó…ìe am …ìen. Pellet, Joomi am ko newanii…óo toppitagol ko O muuyi kon. Pellet, ko Kanko woni Anndu…óo fiyakuuji jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen, √ëee√±u…óo e toppitagol Makko ngol."
  12,101,"Refti yuusufa torii Joomi makko, o maaki: Joomi am, gom…óii A ye…óii lam laamagol Misra, A anndinii lam kadi firo koy…ói. An Tagir…óo kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin e noone mo aldah e yeru gadano, Ko An woni gi…óo heftu…óo denndaangal fiyakuuji am …óin aduna e laakara. ∆≥ettitam tuma lajal am timmata ko mi juul…óo, wa…ótidaa lam e Annabaa…ìe mo∆¥∆¥u…ìe …ìen, immorde e baabiraa…ìe am …ìen e wo…ó…ìe goo, ka Aljanna firdawsi toowu…óo."
  12,102,"Ko jantaa koo e qissa Yuusufa e musi…ó…ìe makko …ìen, Me…óen wahayina …óum e maa…óa, an Nulaa…óo. A anndaano …óum, tawde a tawanooka ka musi…ó…ìe Yuusufa …ìen e…ì…ìunoo werlagol mo ka niwre woyndu, …ìe fewji pewje ma…ì…ìe. Men anndire …óum wahyu on."
  12,103,"Ko …ìuri …óuu…óude e yim…ìe …ìen, hay si a etike, an Nulaa…óo, …ìe gom…óintaa. Wata a na…ìir wonkii maa kin e ma…ì…ìe ninse."
  12,104,"Si …ìe haqqilno, …ìe gom…óinte no tawde a …óa…ì…ìiraali …ìe an Nulaa…óo, e Qur'aanaare nden e ko noddataa- …ìe e mun kon njo…ìdi. Alqur'aana wonaali si wanaa waaju yim…ìe …ìen denndaangal."
  12,105,"∆äuu…óii e Aayeeje tinndinooje bajjin…óingol Alla, saakitaa…óe ka kammuuli e ka leydi, hi…ìe rewa e majje hara ko …ìe …óuurnii…ìe e taskagol …óe waajitora, …ìe ye∆¥∆¥itotaako …óe."
  12,106,"Ko …ìuri …óuu…óude e yim…ìe …ìen gom…óinirtaa Alla wiide ko Kanko woni Tagu…óo, Arsikoowo, Wuurnoowo, Waroowo, si wanaa hara ko …ìe kafidoo…ìe Mo e rewugol rewetee…ói e sanamuuji, …ìe nodditoo wiide Himo jogitii …ìi…ó…óo, senayee woodanii Mo!"
  12,107,"E …ìee sirkoo…ìe hooli nde lepte hippooje arata …ìe ka aduna, …óe suddira …ìe no …ìe waawirtaa du√±ugol …óe maa darngal ngal ardira …ìe juhal, hara kam…ìe …ìe so'aa anndude …óum, sakko …ìe hebiloo ngal, ko …óum ha…ói …ìe gom…óingol?"
  12,108,"An Nulaa…óo, maakan …ìen …ìe noddataa: Ko ngool woni laawol am ngol noddirta yim…ìe …ìen e mun, mi…óo noddira e hoore hujja …ìanngu…óo, yim…ìe jokku…ìe lam …ìen kadi hino noddira non, …ìen feewir…ìe peewal am, …ìe jokki sunna am. Min mi jeyaaka e sirkanoo…ìe Alla …ìen! Ko mi jeyaa, ko e bajjinoo…ìe Mo …ìen Kanko Senii…óo On njyaa mi."
  12,109,"Men Nulaali ado maa an Nulaa…óo, si wanaa wor…ìe …ìanndikoo…ìe …ìe wonaa malaa'ika, Me…óen wahyo e ma…ì…ìe wano Men wahayirta e ma. ∆Åen ko jeyaa…ìe e yim…ìe ca'e …óen …ìe jeyaaka e yim…ìe buruure, yim…ìe ma…ì…ìe …ìen fenni …ìe, Men halki …ìen. E …ìee fennoo…ìe ma yahaali ka leydi, …ìe taskoo ko honno battane fennoo…ìe adinoo…ìe …ìen wa'unoo, …ìe waaji- waajitora …ìen? Pellet ko ko woni kon ka saare laa- laakara e neemaaji, …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥annde …ìen hulunoo- hulunoo…ìe Alla aduna. E on haqqiltaa wonnde ko …óum …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥ude, huliron Alla …óoftagol yamirooje Makko …óen -…ìuri mawnude e majje woni gom…óinal- wo…ó…óito…óon ha…óaa…ói Makko …óin -…ìuri mawnude a majji woni sirkangol Alla."
  12,110,"∆Åen Nulaa…ìe …ìe Men Nulata, Men nennitanay ay…ìe ma…ì…ìe …ìen, Men hawjantaa leptugol …ìe no Men nanngira …ìe doy-doy. Haa ka leptugol …ìe ngol leela …óon, Nulaa…ìe …ìen ta∆¥oo e fii halkugol …ìe ngol, heefer…ìe …ìen fellita wonnde Nulaa…ìe ma…ì…ìe …ìen fenanii…ìe wiide …ìe leptiroyte fennugol ma…ì…ìe ngol, gom…óim…ìe …ìen kan da…óa; ballal Amen ngal arana Nulaa…ìe Amen …ìen, Men da…ónda Nulaa…ìe …ìen e gom…óim…ìe …ìen e halkaare yanaynde e fennu…ìe …ìen. Lepte Amen …óen ruttetaake gaayi e yim…ìe bom…ìe …ìen tuma …óe yanata e ma…ì…ìe."
  12,111,"Gom…óii wonii e qissaaji Nulaa…ìe …ìen e yim…ìe ma…ì…ìe …ìen, e qissa Yuusufa on e musi…ó…ìe makko …ìen, waaju ngu joomiraa…ìe haqqillaaji hisu…ói …ìen waajitorta. Alqur'aana yewtunde fii mun nden wonaali yewtere fefindaande …ìakka e Alla. Ko nde woni, ko goonginnde defte jippiniraa…óe ka Alla …óen, e fensitunde kala ko hatonjini e fensiteede immorde e √±aawooje e sari'aaji, e tinndinnde kala mo∆¥∆¥ere, e yurmeende wonannde yim…ìe gom…óim…ìe nde …ìen; ko kam…ìe nafitorta nde."
